data.description: Welcome to 483 Seneca, a captivating residence nestled in the heart of Richmond Heights, Ohio.  Built in 2016, this meticulously designed home seamlessly blends comfort and style, creating an ideal haven for both families and individuals. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully crafted layout that balances relaxation and entertainment. The main floor boasts a formal front room or office, a spacious family room, a dining room, and an open kitchen. The dining room gracefully opens to a deck and the backyard, enhancing the home's appeal. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, abundant counter space, and a brand-new hood over the range. Upstairs, retreat to the bedrooms, each offering ample closet space, with the main bedroom featuring its ensuite for added convenience. Large windows throughout the home invite natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The property's excellent location ensures easy access to schools, parks, shopping, dining, and the nearby 1-90 highway, making it a prime choice for those seeking both convenience and comfort. This impeccably maintained property exudes pride of ownership and is poised to become your dream home. Don't miss the opportunity to make 483 Seneca your own! OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY, FEBRUARY 18TH 12:00-2:00PM
